articles.author: Jason Rainbow
articles.title: SpaceX Falcon Heavy launches first ViaSat-3 satellite - SpaceNews
articles.description: SpaceX launched the Americas-focused ViaSat-3 broadband satellite on a Falcon Heavy rocket April 30 following delays partly caused by severe weather that included lightning and tornado warnings.
